t of Houston and this right here hits home.  

Recently Frontier has started construction in our city, to lay down and provide fiber for high speed Internet. Up until now, only Comcast XFinity was providing this service and they charged $134/mo for their service with no incentives, even for new customers.  Now Frontier is offering $64/mo and a $200 gift card to switch to them and Comcast is losing their shit.  

I’m not so naïve to think that corporations will be corporations and it’s just a power grab for them in the long run, but I for one like the competition and can appreciate my bills not being so high.  Just pisses me off that Comcast could have charged less for years but only now can “afford” to lower their prices.  

Welcome to America though, right?  End of rant…</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aoJKS9I</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[wisher1977]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My mom, after over two years of my going NC</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Kv6X1qu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wCmj3zS.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7MUyfOa.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TrzGKRZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h4UrcGO.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0dud9XN.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BJnR0eF.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Kv6X1qu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[thecatenelson2283]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The ferocity is on point! Fight for Ukraine</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MCOSgjo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L7BrRXe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9MHwoxq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Not sure what they’re saying but have confirmed it’s genuine. Belarusians fighting for Ukraine!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MCOSgjo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Megolas1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cold artic water kept her in good condition.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FQAukUi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JatHkfk.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div>